## Risk Assessment

| Risk | Likelihood | Impact | Mitigation |
|------|------------|--------|------------|
| Pydantic config fix breaks production config loading | Low | High | Test with actual `.env` file; add unit tests for all `NODE_ENV` values |
| Coverage target (35%) not reachable in timeframe | Medium | Medium | Focus on 0% modules first; 35% is a floor, not a ceiling |
| `datetime.utcnow()` bulk change introduces regressions | Low | Medium | Review each change; use `datetime.now(datetime.UTC)` not `datetime.utcnow()` |
| App archival accidentally breaks active services | Low | High | Only add `DEPRECATED.md` or move to `archive/` — do not delete code |

